      "body" : "I was wondering, if there is no station with the name <code>Station 1</code>, then the <code>filter</code> function returns an empty stream. In that case will it generate a <code>NullPointerException</code> at <code>get().getPassengerCount() </code> ?"
    }, {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 4259399,
        "reputation" : 8416,
        "user_id" : 3484146,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/N411E.jpg?s=256",
        "display_name" : "ifloop",
        "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3484146/ifloop"
      },
      "reply_to_user" : {
        "account_id" : 3908301,
        "reputation" : 820,
        "user_id" : 3234357,
        "user_type" : "registered",
        "accept_rate" : 73,
        "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/9fb6e45e3d6d8f5b205963e0d356711d?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
        "display_name" : "iammrmehul",
